This paper is about multi-label image classification using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of data augmentation techniques and model ensembles, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) research.
